we're gonna let you go in there

317
00:15:13,558 --> 00:15:15,991
without us so you might as
well save your breath, dude.

318
00:15:16,024 --> 00:15:16,958
Koneko too?

319
00:15:16,991 --> 00:15:19,191
There's nothing else goin' on.

320
00:15:20,891 --> 00:15:22,291
