345
00:16:07,258 --> 00:16:08,224
Not like they can stop us.

346
00:16:08,258 --> 00:16:10,891
There are way more of us
than there are of them!

347
00:16:10,924 --> 00:16:12,224
So why are you here...?

348
00:16:12,258 --> 00:16:14,558
I hope it's not for some
sort of rescue operation,

349
00:16:14,591 --> 00:16:16,958
cause if so, you'll have
to deal with me first...

350
00:16:16,991 --> 00:16:19,058
