371
00:17:08,858 --> 00:17:10,791
I bet I'm a sight
for sore eyes, huh?

372
00:17:10,824 --> 00:17:12,058
Yeah, right!

373
00:17:12,091 --> 00:17:14,058
Here's the thing,
I pride myself on the fact

374
00:17:14,091 --> 00:17:17,024
